title: 233: Link’s Strange Physical Therapy Visit | Ear Biscuits Ep. 233
description:
An odd rib injury leads to a strange but enlightening physical therapy session. R&L discuss Link's new interest as well as dive into many other bizarre interests from puppets to eating burnt toast to collecting caution tape from construction sites in this episode of Ear Biscuits!

Note that today’s content was recorded in advance of the US outbreak of COVID-19. Please excuse any reference that is no longer accurate or seemingly disrespectful or unhealthy due to general effects of the COVID-19 pandemic.
